        {
          "context": "服务器上安装x11vnc，构建vnc的服务端：sudo apt-get install x11vnc。设置并存储vnc连接密码为deepin：sudo x11vnc -storepasswd deepin /etc/x11vnc.pass。启动x11vnc服务端：sudo x11vnc -display :0 -auth /var/run/lightdm/root/:0 -forever -bg -o /var/log/x11vnc.log -rfbauth /etc/x11vnc.pass -shared -noxdamage -xrandr \"resize\" -rfbport 5900。",
